data.description:
This home defines custom and quality with touches you cannot find in today's homes, and nestled at the end of the culdesac. The home with 2 stories;first floor  with main bedroom, living/kitchen/dining area, laundry room.  A covered deck is the extension of the main bedroom for some relaxing moments , morning or evening. The entry way has built in cabinet to display your collections. The upstairs has 3 bedrooms ,full bathroom, the landing could be a sitting area/office space/play room . The backyard ! Rock walk way, 
flower garden , wood privacy fence. All the appliances stay to make the move easier. Has new upstairs heat pump , and extra  Blown insulation into the attic. Low utility cost! All electric home
